thread.title: Royal family ‘superfan’ prepares for upcoming wedding

title: Royal family ‘superfan’ prepares for upcoming wedding
text:
Royal family ‘superfan’ prepares for upcoming wedding Thursday, April 05, 2018 - 01:38 
Donna Werner, a self-proclaimed 'superfan' of the British royal family, plans on flying across the sea and camping out on the street for the wedding of Prince Harry and American actress Meghan Markle.
